Instruction: With the battery inserted and PSU panel open, trace the internal wiring from the battery case to the two output terminals and the PSU LED/resistor node. Using a multimeter, measure continuity from the battery positive terminal to the positive output cable contact and to the LED/resistor node, and from the battery negative terminal to the negative output cable contact and LED return node. Also check for 12 V directly at the battery lugs (on the cell itself) to confirm the external measurement point was correct.
