ACTION:
With the PSU panel open and the good 12 V battery installed, functionally test continuity from the battery positive lug to the PSU positive output / LED node using the available test_continuity operation. Systematically probe along the internal path (battery + contact to first pad/trace, then to any fuse/thin trace, then to the output/LED junction) to identify an open circuit or high‑resistance segment that is preventing the 12 V from reaching the LED and output cables.
